{"tid":2641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人幣找換店開出離地擘價！買入價98 賣出價86","createTime":"2016-11-26T00:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T12:59:39.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd900c6f629a172071fa31df20a62529be8964e","tid":2641,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T00:39:35.000Z","msg":"【美元大時代】人幣找換店開出離地擘價！買入價98 賣出價86<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161125&amp;guid=55964281&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161125%26guid%3D55964281%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=zwaEkXe1hEW1tFfMBPrTd8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=0c0d6d15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161125%26guid%3D55964281%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=d4b00e44\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161125&amp;guid=55964281&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161125/280pix/1480061043_bd39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161125%2F280pix%2F1480061043_bd39.gif&h=4bdcee80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於2007年1月11日，人民幣兌港元滙率衝破「1算」後，人仔繼續升值，至2014年才反覆走弱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161125/280pix/1480061148_70c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161125%2F280pix%2F1480061148_70c5.jpg&h=e0d708ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2007年1月11日，香港找換店的人民幣牌價，跌破1兌1算，每1,000港元只能兌998元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161125/280pix/1480065656_89b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161125%2F280pix%2F1480065656_89b2.jpg&h=ba5d64e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前市面上，港元兌人仔牌價約為91及90，屬正常水平。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161125/280pix/1480067365_b5db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161125%2F280pix%2F1480067365_b5db.jpg&h=69c0597c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日旺角有找換店的人民幣買入價為每100人民幣兌109.5元港幣，兌換率即是91.32。（李潤芳攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161125/280pix/1480071426_9fca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161125%2F280pix%2F1480071426_9fca.jpg&h=61c21a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果直擊沙田火車站一家找換店，人民幣買入價為100人民幣兌101.5港幣，賣出價為116.2港幣兌換100人民幣，擘價離奇闊。（王心義攝）"},{"pid":"e0d68ef7a8563600ec3cca83cf66394500357c97","tid":2641,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"人民幣不停貶，現時市面找換店牌價一般每百港元兌90元人民幣左右。本報直擊沙田火車站一家找換店，發現該找換店開出買入價為100人民幣兌101.5港幣（即每百港元兌98.52人民幣），滙價遠較市場價貼近「1兌1」。不過，這個只為找換店開出的人民幣買入價，以欲以較低於現價的水平買入人民幣，實情是找換店開出的人民幣賣出價為116.2港幣兌換100人民幣（即每百港元兌86.05人民幣），即賣出價遠高於現價約90水平。換言之，找換店開出擘價極闊的人民幣買賣價。至於九龍塘火車站的找換店，其兌換率亦和沙田一樣。<br />\n<br />\n至於銀行牌價方面，據中銀香港（2388）兌港元電匯牌價，至下午4時19分，離岸人民幣買入價，每百港元兌89.97元人民幣，賣出價為89.08。至於在岸人民幣買入價為89.61，賣出價為88.77。<br />\n<br />\n目前人民幣實際兌換價仍在每百港元兌90人民幣水平。回顧對上一次人民幣真正平過港元的時代，是早於90年代至00年後，當時人民幣平過港元。其後風水輪流轉，人民幣不斷升值，於2007年1月11日，人民幣兌港元滙率衝破「1算」。翻查報道，當時深圳的食肆、超市及娛樂場所等，均貼出100港元兌90元人民幣的告示，而深圳的士幾乎全部拒收港幣。"},{"pid":"c861493e3965fbab94fb5ce4211f3b098f7f3d0a","tid":2641,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T00:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18486f8bba6f3c02139d44721f404051548d9210","tid":2641,"uid":1699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adeba3aa4dbcc936922627ea361b33132b66c3c","tid":2641,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:19:40.000Z","msg":"條大陸佬英文咁好。不過好鳩煩。講完英文又中文"},{"pid":"f34346959f42a4c31bb242c3da70e29d2869f7a8","tid":2641,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:55:40.000Z","msg":"抵喎"},{"pid":"f5c0656272c01f6eff3d48b6a21e9d09e20371a1","tid":2641,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"呢班友唔想坐艇 應該有d野"}]}